Once upon a time, there was a little boy. He stayed with his parents. His parents were mean to him.Then, he planned to trick his parents.
One night, when his parent went to sleep, Meanwhile, the boys didn't sleep at all. Infact, he put oil with chilli in the glass from which his parents drank. Then he put shaving cream on their faces. Hahaha, he laughed. He also added a toy spider on their noses. The next morning, when his parents woke up, out came a scream. The little boy laughed and went on with his life. He always remembered that day, when he got revenge.
THE END